	// Hot-reload the catalog/policy generation FROM DISK (basil-atq). The broker
	// re-reads the catalog/policy from the same on-disk paths it was started with,
	// runs the full startup/`check` validation, and, on success, atomically swaps
	// in a new generation. This RPC is permission-gated by a dedicated `reload`
